{"tid":1669701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隻警犬唔得啦!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-22T17:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T17:44:04.000Z","uid":263898,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e10120f7f78477fd6f221e2f621198a3ee425a","tid":1669701,"uid":263898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 標題黨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我唔知啲警犬有無事...<br />\n但係再食多幾次彈就一定出事.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以.....點解會完全無人講架！<br />\n聽日1630全部人去狗總抗議啲狗逼啲警犬食彈呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJKTm7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJKTm7X.jpg&h=13a707f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快手啲幫手推呀唔該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毛孩係我地最好嘅朋友尼架！幫佢地發聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祈求食左彈嘅警犬一定要健康無事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9546d5158ef54d8eacbeca89ded5c998ecaacd","tid":1669701,"uid":263898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T17:04:31.000Z","msg":"幫下手推呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as